general_error_rate.title: Error rate
general_error_rate.description: Alignment error rate. Total edit distance (SAM NM field) over the number of mapped bases

N50.title: N50 (Kbp)
N50.description: N50 is the contig length such that using longer or equal length contigs produces half (50%) of the bases of the assembly (kilo base pairs)

Total length.title: Assembly Length (Mbp)
Total length.description: The total number of bases in the assembly (Mbp).

frac_het_phased.title: % Phased Variants
frac_het_phased.description:
Fraction of heterozygous variants
                                          that could be phased.

bp_per_block_avg.title: Avg bp per Block
bp_per_block_avg.description:
Description of the distribution of non-singleton
                                        block lengths, where the length of a block is the
                                        number of base pairs it covers minus 1. That is, a
                                        block with two variants at positions 2 and 5 has
                                        length 3.

block_n50.title: NG50
block_n50.description:
The NG50 value of the distribution of the block
                                        lengths. Interleaved blocks are cut in order to
                                        avoid artificially inflating this value.

config.title: Qualimap BamQC: Genome fraction covered by at least X reads
QUAST: Number of partially predicted genes
